@m_jon_h wrote:

to play on your own just log in with 0.0.0.0 port 5555 but if you wanna advertise and play with other people download hamachi at www.hamachi.cc click create network,enter details etc then tell people to log on to your server with your ham ip and port e.g 5.123.84.73 port 555 but they also have to join the hamachi networks
